name: Amanda Cerny
description:
Amanda Rachelle Cerny is an American Internet personality, actress, and model. She is best known for her YouTube channel and formerly her Vine profile on which she had over 4 million followers. She was Playmate of the Month for October 2011.

Trained on 1.5 base model but examples are on Analog Madness

Skews NSFW as is normal for a playmate, but SFW is easily doable

If you have any comments/criticism/suggestions/or request for the next model in this series or otherwise, please let me know.
